Mpumalanga MEC for education, Bonakele Majuba and learners from some schools in town met Pepper the Robot at the Standard Bank atrium as part of preparations for the fourth industrial revolution. Pepper, the interactive humanoid robot, greeted and danced along with the learners and customers of the bank. Read:
